---
title: American-Style Chicken Tacos with Creamy Charred Corn Slaw & BBQ Mayo
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos – with American-spiced chicken inside no less! The real star of this dish is the BBQ mayo. There’s a smokey hint amidst the expected creaminess of mayonnaise we all know and love, and all of that means you’re in for a burst of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-style-chicken-tacos-20ab7ccc.jpg
